data.description: Welcome to this immaculate 4-bed, 3-bath home, just 3 years young & boasting an open floor plan that effortlessly caters to modern living. The heart of this home is its kitchen, featuring granite countertops, a large walk-in pantry & stainless appliances that stay with the home—including the washer, dryer & fridge. Enhancing its appeal is a spacious 3car garage, perfect for vehicles & storage. Outdoors, the spacious covered lanai overlooks the largest lot in the neighborhood, promising endless possibilities for entertainment & relaxation. Location is prime, w/white sandy beaches just a short drive away. An exceptional offer awaits a qualified VA buyer: the opportunity to assume the seller's mortgage at an attractive rate of 2.75%! Don't miss the chance to make this dream home your reality
